'''巴根遊樂園'''（Dyrehavsbakken）是[[丹麥|丹麥]]首都[[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]郊外的一座[[遊樂園|遊樂園]]，位於哥本哈根以北約10公里處。巴根遊樂園開業於1583年<ref name=bakken>{{cite web | title= The history of Bakken | url= http://www.bakken.dk/english/bakken-the-worlds-oldest-amusement-park | work=  | publisher=  | date= 2015-03-08 | accessdate= 2015-03-08 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150222033757/http://www.bakken.dk/english/bakken-the-worlds-oldest-amusement-park | archive-date= 2015-02-22 | dead-url= yes }}</ref> and is the world's oldest operating amusement park.<ref>{{cite web| title= Oldest amusement part in operation| url= http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/oldest-amusement-park-in-operation/| work= | publisher= | date= | accessdate= 2015-09-01| archive-date= 2021-01-22| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210122124808/https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/oldest-amusement-park-in-operation/| dead-url= no}}</ref>。現在巴根遊樂園平均每年有250至270萬人參觀，是丹麥第二受歡迎的遊樂園<ref>{{cite web| title= Top 25 Attractions in Denmark| url= http://www.visitdenmark.com/usa/en-us/menu/turist/turistinformation/attraktioner/top25attraktioner.htm| work= | publisher= | date= 2009-02-25| accessdate= 2009-04-06| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110224183450/http://www.visitdenmark.com/usa/en-us/menu/turist/turistinformation/attraktioner/top25attraktioner.htm| archive-date= 2011-02-24| dead-url= yes}}</ref>，僅次於[[蒂沃利花園|蒂沃利花園]]。
